     "status" -> "None", "summary" -> 
    "PartitionInto[list, k] partitions list into k non-overlapping sublists \
of equal length. PartitionInto[list, {k1, k2, ...}] partitions a nested list \
into k1*k2*... blocks of equal size. PartitionInto[list, kspec, rest] is like \
Partition[list, nspec, rest] with the nspec determined by kspec so that nspec \
species the lengths of sublists whereas kspec specifies the number of \
sublists.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> "PartitionInto", 
